12 An Act relating to the State Department of Health;
transferring funds to the Barbara Weber Amyotrophic
13 Lateral Sclerosis (ALS) Grant Program Revolving Fund;
providing for noncodification; providing an effective
14 date; and declaring an emergency.
15
16
17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
18 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
19 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
20 Of the Sixty-eight Million Three Hundred Forty-eight Thousand
21 Five Hundred Fifty-eight Dollars ($68,348,558.00) appropriated to
22 the State Department of Health in Section 73 of Enrolled Senate Bill
23 No. 1177 of the 2nd Regular Session of the 60th Oklahoma
24 Legislature, the sum of One Million Dollars ($1,000,000.00) shall be
HB4029 HFLR Page 1
